OL,6,FThe so-called Brit-Cards will allow
OL,7,Fthe verification of a citizen's right
OL,8,Fto live and work in the UK, and are
OL,9,Fexpected to be unveiled by the Prime
OL,10,FMinister during a speech on Friday.
OL,12,FSir Keir is due to speak at the Global
OL,13,FProgress Action Summit in London
OL,14,Falongside Australian prime minister
OL,15,FAnthony Albanese and Canadian prime
OL,16,Fminister Mark Carney.
OL,18,FAnyone starting a new job or looking
OL,19,Fto rent a home would be required to
OL,20,Fshow the card on a smartphone app,
OL,21,Funder the proposals.
