OL,6,FIt would then be checked against a
OL,7,Fcentral database of people entitled to
OL,8,Flive and work in the UK.
OL,10,FIt is hoped this would reduce the
OL,11,Fattraction of working in the UK
OL,12,Fillegally, including for delivery
OL,13,Fcompanies.
OL,15,FBut some are not convinced by the
OL,16,Fproposals, with Nigel Farage's party
