OL,6,FWriting in The Telegraph, Sir Keir
OL,7,Fsaid: "This Government will make a
OL,8,Fnew, free of charge, digital ID that
OL,9,Fwill be mandatory for the right to
OL,10,Fwork by the end of this Parliament."
OL,12,FEarlier this month, the Prime Minister
OL,13,Fsaid an ID card system could play an
OL,14,F"important part" in stopping illegal
OL,15,Fmigration.
OL,17,FA total of 1,157 people have arrived
OL,18,Fon small boats in the last week,
OL,19,Faccording to Home Office statistics.
